text: Glanymor () is an electoral ward for Llanelli Town Council and Carmarthenshire County Council in south Llanelli. The population of this ward at the 2011 censu was 5,668. It consists of the following areas of Llanelli: *Glanymor *Lakeside *Machynys *New Dock ==References== Category:Llanelli Category:Carmarthenshire electoral wards
title: Glanymor
